{"h554b6904g2d5cg4b17g9c7dgaa97a4c809c5": ["You're eager, aren't you? But we need to wait a little longer.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7d08ebe4-eb46-2062-ba65-63d1205d0137"], "hb676e7e5gba9bg4684gb448g1df6dbb6c47a": ["Once everyone's in their bedrolls, we'll slip out of ours and find each other.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ef534ba6-f82f-a7e5-49a7-658e44f36312"], "h3b443794g0539g4e09g8518gdec46ec22a01": ["I hope you're not here to beg. It's so unbecoming. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "25e393d8-a554-60c2-9565-9b91b10412ba"], "h6d6f8c69gc11ag4418g8ddfg9d88d160f307": ["Funny, but unbecoming.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "93d89494-3486-5679-d735-034a3bac39c6"], "h9383a783gce03g4198gbec7g303b8dbf8f0a": ["If you're looking for another shot, I'm afraid you've missed it.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "fd6b9592-46ff-d5ad-23b8-e03f30c1825e"], "h7c6b3c36g68afg4573g8213g691f1933841e": ["You know, I never pictured myself as a hero.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "066d7aca-1f77-37f5-bb79-fece7882f6c9"], "he0ea5cadgc6a4g4eb4g8045g4a4b790d6b46": ["Never thought I'd be the one they toast for saving so many lives. And now that I'm here...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "3c34bbd6-e2df-146f-c09a-6e9ad075215e"], "hd71d36bagdac2g41c5g8ba0g5ef6bdb4671c": ["I hate it. This is awful.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "e245355b-c93f-3432-a21e-464134b240f3"], "hf6b2ea97g9e83g4c34ga986ge0c8e2510b76": ["Really? Saving lives is awful?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "5dc4b077-9be5-e19f-6e98-18a6543c651d"], "h79942740gea8cg4e44gbae7g97212fb52f0d": ["We killed some goblins to save some tieflings. The tally of lives didn't change much.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "96eaf711-4226-e1f5-11a2-26c525f055ed"], "h95260213g74e3g462fgbd37g1c4f376e1819": ["But what do I get for all my hard work? A pat on the head and vinegar for wine.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "2ada58a3-8717-a3a2-9417-37097e3de954"], "h58b760b3g9f46g4c24g9ebfgcdf0518f235f": ["Whinge all you want - I'm having fun.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c4b46cc3-8290-6795-57b3-59930c6a4b39"], "h47968554gb271g46d7ga8d3g6c312bc7076d": ["By all means, go and enjoy yourself.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "9c74aa73-c8b8-da6c-b9bc-4feefde3db5d"], "h88547adfg16aeg4d99ga28bg5d6ae759a6a3": ["I'll be here, waiting for the sunrise.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c80ab3da-a895-791d-bdd3-13fcc947ca4a"], "hb8ff9844g3877g4f30g9410g411b3de1b727": ["True, the goblins would have thrown a wilder party.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "40216f2d-51bc-cbbb-0e1b-99302428f3ac"], "h459fc0bdg4c72g4cfdg9941gcea3b75793ef": ["I'm just looking for a little more excitement. A little more fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "91ac487a-f4e5-37d1-1c4a-9badc6b848c2"], "h7fb1fd7bged34g4281ga58cg0ebd8b36c022": ["And what's your idea of 'a little fun'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "2b8853f7-4c2e-31f5-1e11-739285762852"], "ha0017736g803ag4deag9581g7ff53b631926": ["By the Hells. Sex. Passion. <i>Fun</i>.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7aa6e9b6-0ff2-9cd0-a935-f745c71a1af8"], "h2c013409gca2eg4c9dg9461g7f59e7275014": ["It's easy for some. I see Lae'zel's marked you as her territory.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "343eedab-6143-8e87-68eb-9a5bdf47f52f"], "h17628d7fg2affg49c7gad74g19ea61b29119": ["I just hope she leaves you in one piece. We can't take a week for you to recover from whatever her idea of 'fun' is.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "27f6b605-8292-7058-295c-c75515c2e546"], "hd527ea2ag08e4g48aag8a05g508c1ca04549": ["I'm looking forward to it. It'll be fun.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "022bbbd4-08a4-8724-9e50-10b3a672cd90"], "h31d3125dg0a16g49e4g955bgb21dbad18b4c": ["I'm sure it'll be adequate.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "9b719927-0aac-0ce9-38a9-f5d6402a88c8"], "h172992cagec0bg4698gae15g725a02ba9728": ["But you go ahead. Have <i>fun</i>.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cb1fcdf5-c2f0-3ef6-100c-6ee73a83762d"], "h93e68c44gbc15g41abg9806g4ee578bc24bd": ["It's just sex. Nothing serious.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "3be692d0-2202-758c-c230-7758f6bb8aad"], "h815cdde7gb298g4983gbdadgc618f3b12f3b": ["Serious or not, it's something.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "80faabd6-53a2-8ef0-1bea-9cb56dcb925d"], "hd7d4ad07g560eg41f4g8e92gfdf10b4ee924": ["Feeling jealous, are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c0d20d68-fd23-edb3-36a6-3c4e5be3dc1f"], "h344cf4d3gb414g496fgba06g84564ba4328d": ["Ha! No, my love, I'm not jealous of the beating our gith friend will give you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ceb4c4fa-0957-ccec-93e4-5c0ef201e125"], "he0607d96g0953g4795gb644g9de98b08ebdb": ["Ha! No, my love, you and Shadowheart can get up to whatever you want. It means nothing to me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "9cb21637-20a0-54ad-0bf2-5d6fb7527408"], "h985fbb4dgfc28g4a45gb71cg64336f991be1": ["Ha! No, my love, I'm not jealous of the walking encyclopaedia.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "96eb0372-b36c-7575-a476-727254f76b28"], "h51cd61fag38e7g43c4gabf4g49fda9f1017a": ["Ha! No my love, I'm not jealous of the pup.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1e547994-0fa4-52e3-baa8-082d56e960a5"], "hb1c5bc66g3398g4a0eg9421gd9cc94c74626": ["Ha! No, my love, I'm not jealous of the tiefling.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "104aadf1-7946-a967-a0b8-eb9dac86cff8"], "hf3c72d6cg8db6g4f50gb1adg9863830adba2": ["Ha! Jealous? If you make it through the act without him running off to 'defeat evil', I'll be amazed.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "996d51b7-e035-e0a5-0d20-7d14469f0abf"], "h54021c0cgba7cg4e05g9f86gb8632bad28d4": ["Ha! No. If he had an incubus instead of that cambion? That might be a different story.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ccf1fd34-90bf-c5b3-44b4-3387106bee44"], "he080ce68g8af5g4d1ag8b39g57d84d06e7ac": ["Ha! No, I've seen enough blades in my time.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "be414f66-a9f0-b12c-28fc-c81115eb5346"], "h81149feagee86g4b83g9774g55f953ac7519": ["Are you offering something better? Because I could be persuaded...", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f654cd64-2548-282c-35ce-5a8dab9cc9e1"], "hdf99a9e1g8d21g48f2gb0edg495706e982f9": ["You know, we could always make our own entertainment, darling. Get a little closer, so to speak.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a100aa65-dbb1-2328-fbfc-8aafaa98d28f"], "ha6a295c2g7f11g4e3ag942fgd9c9f981f357": ["It's easy for some. You and Shadowheart seem to have a connection. It looks very sweet.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "540de809-1b2d-55f5-bce3-37dc6432933b"], "hf7c77c33g5e3dg4a4ag8bdcgf898aa23a800": ["Not what I'd call 'passionate', or 'interesting', but sweet.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cb0244a4-e45f-f531-a441-904c4a69efc4"], "h2a142247ge176g4011gb0d7ge795ce3cdc06": ["It's easy for some, of course. You and Gale seem to be getting on very well.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "d0af55b0-b1cb-ef04-d2e4-72a20e21a491"], "hb7090b3bg7cadg4088g96f3g5f1fc6c70761": ["I wonder if he uses magic in the bedroom? That could go very well or very badly.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f14a4205-b1c1-d99b-2ad0-394512ced4fe"], "h0ac1bcdfge377g4ad3g86d6gd30235f0c78d": ["It's easy for some, of course. You and Wyll seem to be getting on very well.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "9ac265da-da6f-1b2c-fe20-00c792cc04eb"], "h9d2482e5ge000g4623g93f0g00520c2e35c9": ["Are you looking forward to seeing his 'Blade of Frontiers'? I hope it's more greatsword than dagger.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c1397d8b-2824-9f56-b5e9-e3421d885434"], "h13a5762dg0872g4f0cga141g2bb5ade4d0d5": ["_", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "0c6a7fd0-125b-9759-7291-437f2f19dfaf"], "h9cdae993g8b2bg4b2bgaf8cgfd2410d42c4a": ["It's none of my business, of course. I wouldn't want to intrude.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "6aaaadb7-ab62-1648-8fe1-2b7ab075d726"], "hdaf095c0g131eg4579gb139g95f1ebc94e40": ["Watch, maybe, but never intrude.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "308b1d81-405b-c25b-c994-f2102a5d6b48"], "h82d85925g8da5g458ag9f79g146d67731b58": ["_", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4ae05008-3966-ae38-f2c6-365c0cff476c"], "he3f40e3eg5be9g4aefgb106g146d24f540b1": ["It's easy for some, of course. You and Karlach seem to be getting on very well.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "30c38768-9e6a-0fe8-161a-61a1e4d5fba5"], "hfb310195gae34g4d96gab8eg723f96823bf3": ["By the Hells. Sex, my dear. A night of passion.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "d6fa66ac-a1bc-30dc-0044-68e6ba52d610"], "hce7155b9gf43ag4999g87c9gebd097703028": ["Not with you, just to be clear.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "c5d0a76b-6ae1-95dd-a54e-20dd19d4d4bc"], "hda2007d8g0549g4946ga66dg6591e2a0c3c8": ["I mean, can you imagine? Urgh. No.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "2a70d2a4-64a7-1ba6-9bf7-9f02a866ff87"], "h04852622g2684g49ccg8a59g91600bc85b7e": ["Anyway, don't let me keep you. I'm sure you have someone else to sniff around. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "76d92a2f-4dfa-1126-ec15-7f1f386e2c07"], "hf4f1e6c6g5d7eg4cd1g8312ge3e21671cc92": ["That had better not mean 'I want to kill something'.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "1588e9ae-8374-3c6c-6c3c-807d6eb55a79"], "hf546d1f8ga9c7g4b5eg808ag64a958d40782": ["Not at all! I was hoping for companionship and - well, maybe a little death. Figuratively speaking.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "95665dc9-8cb3-c0d2-1988-f964ee869263"], "h827739e7gec1cg4c65gbddfg896c38b1c9f3": ["Nothing so dramatic. Just you and me and - well, maybe a little death? Figuratively speaking.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ec6425f1-33ed-74a1-47e1-2953cc7074a1"], "hacceba7bg7b1cg4539gba00ge144932ce7e5": ["We could have fun? We could spend some 'quality time' together.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "67eea55e-1e9e-0b54-5ff4-2e4a167b7be0"], "h625df989g0a6fg461ag9c0bgbf94403294f3": ["Do you think Lae'zel would approve? I saw how she looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a24f6e67-077e-67fb-8954-1eeac11ea42e"], "he0764a29g90e7g4a0cgb75cg3008e5f05af3": ["I'd hate to get between the gith and her trophy. No, I think we'll end this evening as friends.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cf2bb34a-6aa0-14e5-a9e9-d9e593a5fba0"], "h73a8f9bdg65d6g437agb02eg2859b83a5106": ["True, I'd rather lie with them.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "11a7078e-78d1-3aa8-020e-324cf1fcbc42"], "hc761f513g0e1ag4497g864cg070b769df0f6": ["You're not jealous, are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "b9660da8-0f26-0321-e104-4f175c707e25"], "h4939bb2fg5f50g474agaf48ge1d1ac7fc7f4": ["Do you think Shadowheart would approve? I saw how she looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "abbb1076-3fb4-10ef-3ddf-6b356c6a238d"], "h6ffce71cg6f11g4ad1g87b8g50cf9013ce81": ["I don't know what her idea of a good time is, but it seems to involve you. I'd hate to intrude.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "3a0c8923-cdcc-461c-2504-6e06a7e01d54"], "he7ea8f37gd3b5g40bdg914dg10958866e506": ["Do you think Gale would approve? I saw how he looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cfc6c8d5-08ae-8abb-6189-38d2f7de732a"], "h1047e05cgac59g4ed1g88d1ga18d3f280a61": ["No, I wouldn't want to get in the middle of whatever that is. We'll end tonight as friends.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "bd5e32f3-7eb5-1f2f-16e0-57dfa14a48c0"], "h21ba8287gc022g4afcg988fg4a3f2ece8bd4": ["_", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "e15a45bb-e0c4-3cf2-70ae-809d537981e4"], "h2cad17fdg0becg4c67gb393g966dbab0eeab": ["Do you think Karlach would approve? I saw how she looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cbcfbd0b-b092-7959-5ecc-2775169863f3"], "h3986bbf7g5d02g42a0g9325ged4087b3c60a": ["_", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "f1d2ef6a-aacb-3d15-5834-9998dc1aafed"], "h9b896f24gc029g48c2g9109g52c94603beb2": ["Do you think Wyll would approve? I saw how he looked at you earlier.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "14bdaed6-25c4-6d60-ae10-116dfb8d9e32"], "hf5bb97e1g3919g4833gaf79g2de8a9afcbce": ["Well, that'd certainly spice up this evening.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "389fc18d-9692-3395-4236-c85e50f0f17a"], "h5f09d760g8665g47edg9709gef45e7348c37": ["Let's wait until things quieten down. Once the others are asleep, we'll find each other. ", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "64348e36-77dc-1044-a5f2-13dabdfb9273"], "ha9a7e2fcg5123g411agbefbgc4be73d1b983": ["All right, let's do it. I'll see you later.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "9f89b2aa-f106-d05e-0a15-154c72012c04"], "hba49502eg285dg437bgaf43g7b95018d5242": ["Indeed you will, my love. Indeed you will.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "776359d7-027e-15b0-01b1-88e8c05b7583"], "h9a071395g5c8cg41b3ga75bgfa9201b855eb": ["I'm not sure. Let me get back to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "77c149db-74e0-2fb8-6a3d-ee9611bfe878"], "h405a0f23g40c4g4f2dgbf38gc2411ca589c6": ["All right, but don't take too long. You're not the only tasty morsel around here.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "7e68ff18-0c72-cfe4-7737-6dd23cb10d01"], "heee18e52gba5ag476eg870agc7997bbe6b22": ["On second thoughts, maybe not.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a45d23aa-af2f-4b8b-a832-8c2ea33fde6c"], "hf7401377g8dbag43afg9fd6g2a31409c3c9c": ["Never listen to your second thoughts. They always spoil the fun.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "945760e9-a4db-0daa-3de7-57d94f8de8b0"], "hae40f904g4e1ag4402g99b6g8af68b3b641e": ["But fine. If you're determined to ruin your evening, I won't stop you.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "b2dcc870-9b74-50f3-12cb-969a9971b787"], "h3144d2abg8d14g4eaeg90aega7591355223f": ["I'm flattered, but I think not. It's not you, you understand, it's me.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "99e93af2-7e5b-67fd-06d5-fe7a095c393e"], "h0d2df72fg18aag4348gb412g47cf679f664f": ["I have standards.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "e473005d-f9fd-883e-b4af-9ad8248a74ee"], "h6ae46ab8gd010g49e1ga6acg7867d895bf0f": ["Knowing you, it probably is.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "a22cd389-4dbf-195b-8623-7ef244a737ff"], "h26987f8dg1ef1g4b50gab55g412c827571cd": ["Don't be so sour. I like a good time as much as anyone.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "4dbba99e-ff42-b757-85b3-33b4e4adf5e3"], "h939c033bg425ag4f5egac94g2285bed9b755": ["I'd rather bed a goblin, <i>darling</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "ca76dfb0-c50f-4d36-0675-38b17c3f3ba5"], "h35216675g4be1g469agaf2eg2d99fcffbedd": ["You are an insolent little pup, aren't you?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "91557ef6-1a49-b34a-da88-dafc536c51d7"], "h3dbf1b37g9c94g4044g81dcge33f91e91c0e": ["But have it your way. I'm happy to entertain myself.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "cd3e21f5-54fd-c7ea-b0e5-5580de9df482"], "h3bbf4451gc697g4622g9090g724b0be71ce0": ["No, absolutely not.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Camp_Relationship_Dialogs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntTieflingCelebration_CRD_Astarion.html", "213a5619-5bc1-5d6e-bc13-3912299c2429"], "h0f030b6fg7affg4647gaadegb12ce3f3e609": ["And here I mistook you for someone with taste. A pity.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialog